title: Moist vegan fruit cake
ingredients: ['500g plain flour', '400g caster sugar', '4 tablespoons unsweetened cocoa powder', '2 tablespoons cornflour', '2 teaspoons bicarbonate of soda', '1 teaspoon salt', '2 teaspoons ground cinnamon', '2 teaspoons ground cloves', '750g unsweetened apple sauce', '175ml vegetable oil', '150g raisins', '175g chopped pitted dates', '450g crystallised mixed fruit', '240g chopped walnuts', '60g walnut halves', '170g halved glace cherries']
